data.eml:eml: A new species of whitefly (Hemiptera: Aleyrodidae) and its parasitoid (Hymenoptera: Aphelinidae) from desert lavender in California

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Polaszek, Andrew, Gill, Raymond (2011): A new species of whitefly (Hemiptera: Aleyrodidae) and its parasitoid (Hymenoptera: Aphelinidae) from desert lavender in California. Zootaxa 2750: 51-59, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.203137
